OL,3,CStaff at yacht manufacturer facing
OL,4,C'temporary lay-off' due to operational
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FA luxury yacht manufacturer based in
OL,8,FDorset has confirmed around 100 staff
OL,9,Fhave been 'temporarily laid off' as it
OL,10,Fstruggles to deal with operational
OL,11,Fissues.
OL,13,FSunseeker International in Poole said
OL,14,Fthat the employees were placed on a
OL,15,Flay-off on 2 and 3 January, but are
OL,16,Fexpected to return to work by 27
OL,17,FJanuary.
