OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,F"During the temporary lay-off period,
OL,8,Feach employee will receive 50% of
OL,9,Ftheir normal basic hourly rate in an
OL,10,Feffort to minimise any personal
OL,11,Fdifficulties during this time.
OL,13,F"We are speaking to affected employees
OL,14,Fto explain the circumstances. It's
OL,15,Fimportant to state that no permanent
OL,16,Femployee has lost their job.
OL,18,F"We reiterate how important all our
OL,19,Fstaff, their knowledge, skills and
OL,20,Fcraftsmanship are to us.
