OL,7,F"We appreciate their loyalty and
OL,8,Fpatience at this time."
OL,10,FIt comes two weeks after the Unite
OL,11,FUnion claimed that 250 workers with
OL,12,Fless than two years' service at the
OL,13,Ffirm were to lose their jobs.
OL,15,FThe union vowed to work to get the
OL,16,Fdecision reversed
OL,18,FIn November Sunseeker was sold by its
OL,19,FChinese owners to two investment firms.
